{"tid":1656691,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法就快過，我地要再次多謝勇武不離不棄","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T03:56:37.000Z","uid":151057,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5341291ae4af2ccd51cbb065f62d1bbe9a515ef1","tid":1656691,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"做文宣的我地<br />\n心諗如果唔係有勇武為香港付出人生<br />\n單靠和理非同班失敗軍師<br />\n今日係唔會成功打擊到政府<br />\n<br />\n雖然之前有三毛成功帶風向話<br />\n「勇武搞到文宣跟唔切」<br />\n導致有部份善良勇武暫時收咗一下手<br />\n<br />\n我地相信就算人權法過咗<br />\n革命仲未會即刻成功<br />\n就算之後勇武射飛彈<br />\n我哋都會繼續為一切行動文宣<br />\n永遠唔會責備<br />\n<br />\n原本以為上周日已經俾班<br />\n連登HK01旗下帶風向禁勇武<br />\n會令人灰心 但原本冇人放棄<br />\n所以我地更應該永遠都係勇武嘅支援"},{"pid":"9adab2db77afd787eea4a2a7f3c38c346010619f","tid":1656691,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b8b083cba4f2bf263d510fa2a2663b1d0b4085d4","tid":1656691,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c624628be30f44c942fc9cd26c56a2d9bbcda202","tid":1656691,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRw9ttS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRw9ttS.jpg&h=a70b0641&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65c0cf5695886134f80a33d1555d544bd076aaf1","tid":1656691,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src